- VSCode Version: 1.10.2 (1.10.2)
- OS Version: macOS 10.12.3

Steps to Reproduce:

1. Open a new `scss` file with code below

```css
@mixin test {
    color: red;
    @error 'Test';
}
```

Expected
No errors should be reported

Current
Two errors are reported

```bash
[scss] } expected
[scss] at-rule or selector expected
```
